<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- bfḍl nʿmtk .. wʿmq rḥmtk
 ậty lmḥbtk .. wạrtmy ʿlyk
 ạrwi ẓmạ̉ qlby .. wsẖwqy wḥby
 frạḥty yạ rby .. wḥạjty ạ̹lyk
 ạlqrạr- tḥmdk ạlsẖfạh .. wtnḥny ạljbạh
 lsẖkẖṣk yạ ạllh .. fạ̉nt kẖạlqhạ
 tsbḥ ạlqlwb .. ạ̉mạmk tdẖwb
 fạsmk mhwb .. wạ̉nt sydhạ
 2- ạ̹lhy mạ ạ̉bhạk .. mạ ạ̉ʿẓm gẖnạk
 fʿysẖy fy rḍạk .. sẖwqy wldẖty
 ldẖạ ạ̉ntẓrk .. wʿyny nḥwk
 wtḥt ẓlk .. tṭyb jlsty
 3- ạ̹lhy ṣkẖrty .. ḥṣny qwty
 wkl bhjty .. bqrbk yswʿ
 yạ frḥty bk .. fzt bḥbk
 wqrb qlbk .. ạ̉ḥbk yswʿ</lyrics>
<title>bfḍl nʿmtk</title>
